5:

bad.

we're working security, so it's not

15:
Were we to be attacked by

29:
You betcha! Leave this to Feanie, the

37: Wh-what in theâ€”what is this power...
41:
*yawn*

Thanks to you, we had another

76:
That I do. There's someone I'd like

97:
Distantly, yes... But I also only

100:

106:
I-I'm sorry... But if I don't save up

112:
I wanna see Mama too... I don't

117:
Er... Albert... Can we assume that

127:
Me and Papa were searching all
over for her, but...
130:

147:

151:

156:
Do you guys know where my mama

160:
Sorry... We're in the dark there, just

164:
But we should be able to help you

169:
Would you like to come with us,
Feanie?
174: Don't worry. You can trust them.
184:
U-um, you can have all this money 
if you take me with you!
189:
Ha. Look at the brat trying to be all
considerate.
193:
You should use that money on
something YOU want, Feanie.
196:
We will help you find your mother
and father. Until then, you are
welcome to stay in Starview Village.
206: Thank you... We are in your debt.
211:
I'll be sure to be a good girl and help
out lots and lots to pay you all back!
